{
  "stem": "10572.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a ghostly-- it was on a-- we were on a planet that was beyond any description and any-- And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I, I thought that day and the next day-- I said, if any one of us escape here to tell the world--",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] we had five barracks, the Juden Baraken, the 'Jew barracks.' And the 11,000 were put in those five barracks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were like herrings, or sardines, next to each other, those four stories.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Pictures of them-- pictures that are known today, were shown in And the unbelievable thing was that the first couple of days we're not doing anything.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were standing outside the barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was raining.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some people were-- had used their hats to catch the rain, hoping that they would catch enough rain to wet their tongues.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And during those first three nights-- three days-- we saw many-- and some of our friends-- lose their mind and go berserk.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some of them jumped into the open latrines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Dante's It was hell like it had never been described.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And nobody could describe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And many other things that I've read later on about it-- it is impossible to describe all of those things.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe by trying to do crazy things and being myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw, after I was there for about a week, I saw a kapo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A 'kapo' comes from the Italian, 'head.' And they use this from the Italian fascists, this term, because Mussolini also had concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the kapos were professional criminals, professional criminals who, when they had served their term, the Gestapo would pick them as anti-social.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
